Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.39,0:00:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他乘客呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都下車了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下車…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在輪到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在等你喲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(化貓)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(物怪)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.74,0:01:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色的月光照着你徘徊的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想說的話卻說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.45,0:01:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日子令人如此不耐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猶記那虛偽的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.79,0:01:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘卻那溫暖的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.33,0:01:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有如失了魂的空虛眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.17,0:01:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映照着什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.11,0:01:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛幻的下弦月隱臟在雲間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗如今正慢慢浮現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,述說着真相
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁抱着孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚只能夠幽幽嘆息嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.80,0:02:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(大結局)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,列車是不會停的，除非…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.27,0:02:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直待在這…\N不要！我不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.85,0:02:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快想點辦法吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定辦得到吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.62,0:02:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.56,0:02:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想替後輩報仇…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…想替節子小姐報仇？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯！幫那個被殺的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.57,0:02:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市…川…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森…谷…先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過份的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.33,0:03:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是貓呈現出來的嗎？\N看着吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刻劃在現場的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.72,0:03:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從記憶中得到“理”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.39,0:03:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“理”則喚出因果與淵源
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.03,0:03:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是妳不好~\N“形”、“真”與“理”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃至轉生之地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就請您讓我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.65,0:04:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“理”之景象吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？妳說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說福田市長貪污！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(每朝日報)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經掌握到報導的題材了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.27,0:04:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來聽聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森谷…先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的掌握到內幕了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市長先生\N頻頻與鐵路公司的董事見面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是掌握到非常可靠的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這樣還不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這種時候面談\N不好意思，市川
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看也知道不對勁吧\N我們可不是什麼三流的週刊雜誌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能只憑這點情報\N就刊登妳的報導
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上雖然這麼說\N其實你是在忌妒我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忌妒？妳說誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是說森谷先生…忌妒我囉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我爆出頂級的料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.54,0:05:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算哪門子的爆料啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.98,0:05:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼忌妒啊眼紅什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.98,0:05:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人才會說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來派妳去跑新聞是一大失敗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是白忙一場
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳回去報家庭版吧\N我不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會放棄的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對會讓它變獨家的\N別搞錯了，市川
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.83,0:05:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這樣根本沒有身為記者的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(吉祥料亭)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女色狼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間…逆轉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝…\N小心走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.92,0:05:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們單獨談談吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:05:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣還不能上報嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如我所料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.72,0:06:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道妳一定辦得到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請原諒我對妳說了那麼嚴厲的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒我吧！市川
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，我對那傢伙很賞識
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.59,0:06:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才對她特別嚴厲…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼時候的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片都是妳自已拍的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,底片呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，到外面去談吧\N咦，可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…可是獨家啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳應該不想讓別人知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是報社裡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.99,0:06:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(康康咖啡廳)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.82,0:07:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是市長與東都電鐵的董事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.99,0:07:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後是日本橋建設的社長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地點都是在吉祥料亭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市長為了替東都電鐵\N大開便利之門而通過條例
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.61,0:07:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該收了不少賄賂當作回報
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.44,0:07:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪家銀行？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市井銀行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市長的叔叔曾是那裡的總經理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然已經掌握那麼多的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就好辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就把這件事報導出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交稿的時間是明天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後天用頭版的方式刊登
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒什麼時間，妳辦得到吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報導…由我全權負責？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這新聞是妳自已跑出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是由妳執筆啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前誤會森谷先生您了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為您一直覺得我是個\N輕浮又沒用的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為我不可能\N跑出什麼像樣的新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來\N我也能成為第一線的新聞記者了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道“此方旅館”嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那裡寫稿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我閉關寫稿嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.92,0:08:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這篇報導千萬別讓任何人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排版也由我親自做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.46,0:08:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯我是上次打電話來的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我有點事情想跟您談談
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.27,0:08:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，不算是什麼好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:08:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，刻意到其他地方見面\N可能不太妥當
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會親自登門拜訪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.12,0:09:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“理”  …越來越接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，你說可以讓我\N在電影裡出現是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託嘛，我很想出名啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說~什麼\N也不要在這裡窩一輩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(市政府)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你那兒的人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚可是讓我嚐到睽違許久…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇破膽的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:09:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(此方旅館)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:10:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好，這裡是此方旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(開什麼玩笑，那個臭老太婆)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(一天到晚照顧老人\N我哪受得了啊…)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(因為有那個人)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(我才有勇氣活下去)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有您的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(節子  真討厭真討厭)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.57,0:11:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(一輩子過着抬不起頭的生活)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是夠悲哀…的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那種喪家之犬不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是個新聞記者呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我是市川…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？這是為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(康康咖啡廳)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(千代)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人問過我要不要當歌手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.12,0:11:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，當時…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼會拒絕呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森谷先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.48,0:12:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒有被人跟蹤吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.25,0:12:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…你是怎麼了森谷先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼抖成那樣啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這個題材\N可是很厲害的獨家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會\N又沒有人會追殺我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是替那傢伙着想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去給她一點忠告而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼性急
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原稿呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.85,0:13:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要在這地方看嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.66,0:13:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼？\N(森谷這原稿不能見人)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這新聞不能登\N為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(把它燒了)\N這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰的命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正男！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正男，快起床！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森谷先生，你太過份了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.38,0:13:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這根本就是越權！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟上頭報告！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的，我已經跟上頭報告過了\N你騙人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有騙妳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從一開始就打算這麼做對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一開始你就想搶走我的原稿\N無藥可救…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真卑鄙！騙子！\N真是沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一開始就打算那麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會去找她談談
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼談？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛！我要跟社長說！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等着被解僱吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.51,0:14:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事多少會帶來點麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過應該沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正交給你處理就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嫉妒妳？\N可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笑死人！\N可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.75,0:14:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會在意那種小事呢\N可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.55,0:14:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不過是個女人\N可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關鍵時刻腦筋就死板板的\N可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.86,0:14:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…只是把眼光…放得比較遠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓開通典禮蒙上任何陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一不小心就會變成醜聞的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成你跟福田市長…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.28,0:14:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…\N妳說呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.95,0:14:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…\N女人就是見識淺短啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.12,0:14:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是不會看情勢做事呢\N原來從一開始你就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.59,0:14:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不打算報導那則新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後只要妳肯乖乖聽我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:15:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把新聞送到其他報社去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手上還有其他證據
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正笨的人是你喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.81,0:15:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.91,0:15:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不會給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.75,0:15:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在這時候\N我才覺得自已活着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市民不會原諒你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要妳消失就沒問題了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手住手啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個臭老太婆…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼不快點死啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是個笨女人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧我還想給她忠告呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果卻自已…\N自已找死？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.02,0:16:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意氣風發的女記者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為夢想破滅而自殺嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛，好痛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體動彈不得…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開…開什麼玩笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.01,0:16:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看到我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這怠忽職守的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.42,0:16:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快發現我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒不了你…饒不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這連小篇幅的報導都排不上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.05,0:17:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想當女明星…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.18,0:17:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的酬勞…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯這是自殺，是自殺啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.63,0:17:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.90,0:17:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在於宇宙之間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類存在於世上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若要幻化為物怪之形
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:18:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須依附人類的因果與淵源\N而形成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然一旦出現於世間之物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就非斬不可
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此處已成為…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.04,0:18:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化貓的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故需…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淨化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅除
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮壓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解.放
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夢嗎？\N市民也對此翹首以盼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望二期工程能夠盡快進行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬歲…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.85,0:19:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是白日夢嗎？一點也不像
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.25,0:19:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，市川
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別恨我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.82,0:19:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.57,0:20:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒不了…你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滅！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當你不在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無法笑得開懷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是如此被你吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.23,0:20:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在隨處可見的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些無可取代的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.37,0:20:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能夠好好珍惜地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.25,0:20:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就已經別無所求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.73,0:21:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨風緩緩飄落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.94,0:21:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星光落在那早已看不見的夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.51,0:21:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那段日子\N也令人珍愛到無可比喻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生於世
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪亦生於世
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.70,0:21:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦妖怪與人之
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.77,0:21:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“真”與“理”相呼應
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便可得到“形”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得其形
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.81,0:21:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將幻化成不得存於世上的物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪無法根絕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.98,0:21:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻可斬除
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:21:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故而退魔劍存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.59,0:22:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用劍之人亦存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.69,0:22:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以各位
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.49,0:22:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的“真”與“理”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.86,0:22:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請仔細道來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.23,0:22:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪尚存於人世之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.67,0:22:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到會發生\N這麼不可思議的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.37,0:22:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.51,0:22:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…來了~
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(謝謝觀賞)
